294.speaker: PANDA
294.definition: so could you make a fool of yourself? I'd rather not.

295.speaker: PANDA
295.character: じゃあ 道頓堀川に飛び込んでよ
295.definition: Then could you jump into the Doutonbori River?

296.speaker: PENGUIN
296.character: 飛び込みたくないかな
296.definition: I'd rather not. You're so conservative, Mr. Penguin.

297.speaker: PENGUIN
297.character: 一度キミとはじっくり話したいと思ってたんだけどさぁ
297.definition: I've always wanted to have a realconversation with you just once...

300.speaker: POLAR BEAR
300.character: 来週のしろくまカフェはラジオのみでお送りします
300.definition: Next week's Polar Bear's Café, will be brought to you by radio only.

301.speaker: PENGUIN
301.character: テレビのみでお送りします
301.definition: It'll be brought to you by television only.
